des: KGAY is Palm Springs locally owned and operated LGBT+ radio station playing Dance Hits with local personalities, mix shows and information on many Palm Springs area events. Serving the LGBTQ+ community for over four years with Dance Hits from disco to now KGAY is a favorite worldwide. Visiting Palm Springs? Find KGAY on FM at 106.5 and be sure to check out kgaypalmsprings.com and gaydesertguide.lgbt forCoachella Valley event listings.
